                "text": "Phase 5 m4-002: array literal expressions with explicit syntax `[expr, expr, ...]` require a type annotation to disambiguate the element type when the array is empty. Provide an explicit type annotation like `let xs: [u64; 3] = [1, 2, 3];` or ensure the array is not empty so the type can be inferred from elements."
